title: Monacow 2005.
name: Monacow 2005.
description:
A Map by Generalsmuts

Monaco says:
&quot;A fantastic impression! The cows let loose in the Principality next summer will leave no one indifferent. They will bring beauty, brilliance, movement and animation, all impregnated with, elegance, cleverness, humour, charm or poetry. They will delight residents and visitors, man and women, young and old people.

The &quot;MonaCow Parade&quot; will offer the whole Monegasque population the possibility of taking part in an exhibition that will once again allow placing the Principality in the foreground.

The institutions, the societies, the associations, the shopkeepers, the companies, private citizens and students, in a word, all the local actors will associate to make the Principality the site of one of the largest open air exhibitions in Europe.

Arts. By giving artists, known or not, the possibility of expressing themselves in an unexpected manner, we will all take part in the Principality's cultural radiation.&quot;

Summer 2005.
